<plot>A funny and unlucky man lives in a Bulgarian village in the 1930s. He is cheated at the market, his wife admonishes him, villagers mock at him, and he dreams of being a venerable gentlemen. Well, one day, clad in a brilliant suit, he finds himself in a big town. He faces hypocrisy, mercantilism, and roughness. A helpful lessons teaching him to view his own delusions with self-irony.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?220721</url></doc>
